    "Also, note that the Partially Extended Views experiment failed to translate two more simple NL questions than Conceptual Schema Views experiment.",
    "One explanation is that LLMs are non-deterministic; if the experiments were repeated several times, Table 6.2 could report slightly different accuracy results for Conceptual Schema Views and Partially extended views experiments.",
    "A comparison between the results of the Partially Extended Views and Fully Extended Views experiments shows a decrease of 8%.",
    "Indeed, the fully extended views save more joins, facilitating the Text-to-SQL task, but they require passing much larger view specifications in the prompt.",
    "Furthermore, the definition of a fully extended view, which combines several views, requires renaming several columns, which may create columns with similar names."
